        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎥 Footage Cleanup & Grade\n\nRescue shaky, noisy phone footage with deterministic FFmpeg filters — no AI.\n\n**Pipeline:** Video → stabilize → denoise → boost saturation → output.\n\n**Try this:** raise `smoothing` for steadier (but more cropped) motion, lower `strength` if denoising smears detail, and nudge `saturation` toward 1.3 for pop."
